1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the ongoing compliance monitoring,
 third-party assurance evaluation,
 and vendor remediation framework for vendors,
 contractors,
 and third-party service providers engaged with Elko County information systems.
\end_layout

