\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The vendor name and all associated contracts or service agreements.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The asset support classifications (IT-Managed,
 IT-Supported,
 or Vendor-Managed) applicable to the vendor's services as defined in Policy 1.12 (IT Asset Management Policy).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The data classification tier of data the vendor accesses or processes as defined in Policy 1.11 (Data Governance and Classification Policy).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Whether the vendor has logical or physical access to Criminal Justice Information (CJI).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The current CJIS Security Addendum status,
 where applicable.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The vendor SLA performance data maintained under Policy 3.02 Section 6.5.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
All enforcement notifications received from Policy 5.01.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
All third-party assurance evidence received and evaluated under Section 6.4.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The outcome of each vendor compliance review conducted under Section 6.2.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The status of any active Corrective Action Plan (CAP) associated with the vendor under Policy 5.03.
\end_layout

